{
  "stem": "7157.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What I recall and what I've been told is very difficult to separate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in some cases I recall.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In some cases, I've been told some of these things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the bad things really started in our area like in 1938.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We at this point already were forced out of Breslau-- Wroclaw, the city-- in our apartment.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had to relocate in-- in Poland, because Germany was already taking pieces of Poland at that time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we essentially were relocated, or we moved to another part of Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't-- I don't recall, and I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were very Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Especially my grandparents, the Glotzers, were very Jewish and kosher.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father was a little what we'd probably call today on the reform conservative side.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Traditional more than anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whether they belonged to a temple, I don't-- I don't recall.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I don't-- I certainly don't have any memories of being in a synagogue prior to 1938, from my age of zero to three.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was, as I said, in '38.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we moved into Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because basically, we were moving east.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The idea was to move east away from the Germans, towards the Russians.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This kind of a move was, you know, you typically-- maybe you've seen it in movies or read in books about it-- it was by wagon.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was by foot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were no trains, at least not for us at that point.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was a very difficult move.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our first move was really to our grandparents' home, the Glotzers, who already lived in Poland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What was more-- what was also difficult for me, George and I, actually-- that we spoke German.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our first language was German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Being born on the border like that, German was the language.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
